<s> Thanks for the suggestions in the meeting last week, and on the list since then, for a new slide in the online overview, describing "What is Web Accessibility." I'd also mentioned that I was going to ask the WAI team for comments on the slides, and Ian pointed out that the slides in the online overview mainly focus on accessibility of Web sites, and that we need to also emphasize the need for accessibility of the software used to access and produce Web content.  </s>
<s> Throwing some of these thoughts together, how about something like the following?  </s>
<s> This could become slide 3, right at the beginning of the slide  </s>
<s> set.  </s>
