<s> Hello Judy and all, I find this slide clear as a whole.  </s>
<s> Nevertheless, I have problems with the second sub-bullet of the first list.  </s>
<s> If you ignore the first sub-bullet, it sounds as follows: Web accessibility includes: - making Web sites accessible to people with disabilities, by making them: -- for people with disabilities that can encounter barriers on the Web.  </s>
<s> I suggest: Web accessibility includes: - making Web sites accessible to people with disabilities, that can encounter barriers on the Web. -- by making Web sites more perceivable, operable, navigable, understandable and robust.  </s>
